(6, 'تعریف متغیر ها در javascript', '<p class="MsoNormal" dir="RTL" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\nline-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt"><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;">در علم کامپیوتر ، داده هر چیزی است که برای کامپیوتر معنی دارد.\r\nجاوا اسکریپت هشت نوع داده مختلف را ارائه می دهد که که عبارت هستند از: </span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">undefined</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span>،</span><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"> </span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">null</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span>،</span><span lang="FA" style="font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;"> </span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">boolean</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span>، </span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:\r\n14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">string</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span>،\r\n</span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">symbol</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span>، </span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:\r\n14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">bigint</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span>،\r\n</span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">number</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span> و </span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:\r\n14.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">object</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span>.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" dir="RTL" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\nline-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt"><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;">به عنوان مثال ، رایانه ها بین اعداد مانند شماره </span><span dir="LTR"></span><span dir="LTR"></span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;B Nazanin&quot;"><span dir="LTR"></span><span dir="LTR"></span>12</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span>\r\n<span lang="FA">و رشته ها مانند "</span></span><span dir="LTR"></span><span dir="LTR"></span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;"><span dir="LTR"></span><span dir="LTR"></span>12</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span>"\r\n، "</span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;">dog</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span>" یا "</span><span dir="LTR"></span><span dir="LTR"></span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;"><span dir="LTR"></span><span dir="LTR"></span>123</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span> </span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;">cat</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span>" که مجموعه ای از\r\nکاراکترها هستند ، تمایز قائل می شوند. رایانه ها می توانند عملیات ریاضی را بر روی\r\nاعداد انجام دهند ، اما روی رشته ها نمی توانند.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" dir="RTL" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\nline-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt"><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;">متغیرها به رایانه ها اجازه می دهند داده ها را به روشی پویا ذخیره\r\nو دستکاری کنند. آنها این کار را با استفاده از "برچسب" انجام می دهند تا\r\nبه جای استفاده از خود داده ها، به داده ها اشاره کنند. هر یک از این هشت نوع داده\r\nممکن است در یک متغیر ذخیره شود.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" dir="RTL" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\nline-height:normal;tab-stops:45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt"><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&quot;Courier New&quot;">متغیرها مثل متغیرهای </span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&quot;B Nazanin&quot;">x</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span> <span lang="FA">و </span></span><span dir="LTR" style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;">y</span><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span><span style="font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;"><span dir="RTL"></span><span dir="RTL"></span>\r\n<span lang="FA">هستند که در ریاضیات از آنها استفاده می کنید ، به این معنی که آنها\r\nیک اسم ساده برای نمایش داده هایی هستند که می خواهیم به آنها مراجعه کنیم.\r\nمتغیرهای رایانه با متغیرهای ریاضی فرق دارند زیرا می توانند مقادیر مختلفی را در زمان‌های\r\nمختلف ذخیره کنند.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" dir="RT