(9, 'اختصاص مقدار یک متغیر به دیگری', '<p class="MsoNormal" dir="RTL"><span lang="FA" style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-ansi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;B Nazanin&quot;">بعد از اینکه مقداری با استفاده\r\nاز عملگر انتساب به یک متغیر اختصاص یافت ، می توانید مقدار آن متغیر را با استفاده\r\nاز عملگر انتساب به متغیر دیگری اختصاص دهید.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p align="right">\r\n\r\n<table class="MsoTableGridLight" dir="rtl" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-width: initial; border-style: none;">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width="623" valign="top" style="width: 467.5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-color: rgb(191, 191, 191); padding: 0cm 5.4pt;">\r\n  <p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  text-align:left;line-height:18.0pt;background:#FFFFFE;direction:ltr;\r\n  unicode-bidi:embed"><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Consolas;\r\n  mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:blue">var</span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  color:black">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Consolas;\r\n  mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00107E">myVar</span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  color:black">;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n  <p class="MsoNormal" dir="LTR" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n  text-align:left;line-height:18.0pt;background:#FFFFFE;direction:ltr;\r\n  unicode-bidi:embed"><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Consolas;\r\n  mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00107E">myVar</span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  color:black">&nbsp;=&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:\r\n  Consolas;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#098658